sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant C as Client (CLOSED)
    participant S as Serveur (LISTEN)

    Note over C,S: Three-way handshake TCP — RFC 793

    C->>S: SYN (seq=x)
    Note left of C: état → SYN_SENT

    S-->>C: SYN, ACK (seq=y, ack=x+1)
    Note right of S: état → SYN_RECEIVED

    C->>S: ACK (seq=x+1, ack=y+1)
    Note left of C: état → ESTABLISHED
    Note right of S: état → ESTABLISHED

    Note over C,S: Connexion établie — échange de données possible
